parameters: \N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>What are you doing here, in a place like this?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Heh, have you reached the age where you're starting to know
about such things?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Look at what's happening inside... You already understand,
don't you? Your mother... it's the work of a vixen.

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>A vixen who deceives men and swindles their money. Who
would've thought she'd go this far, with such an innocent
face she's quite something.

\N<Riia>...What are you doing here, Auntie? Do you need something
from me?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Hehe... You've got a cute face when I look closely. You
really are that woman's son.

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Have you had any experience with that sort of thing yet? If
you'd like, how about graduating with me?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Hmph, you're an unpleasant brat just like your mother. Get a
little kindness and you start getting cocky.

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Well, whatever. Just remember, I will never forgive you and
your mother, you hear?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>I'll hate you forever. I'll drag you down. I'll curse you
every single day and night.

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Oh, that's right. Your childhood friend... Rame, was it? I
heard a rumor that she's also stuck with Rozaro and moved to
the city where the Luda headquarters are.

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>By now she might be spreading her legs for Rozaro or maybe
she's being raped by Luda soldiers and crying about it?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Hehe, serves her right. That's what she gets for meddling in
another family's affairs, isn't it?

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Remember this, your mother and child's misfortune has only
just begun.

\N<Hojiko's Ex-Wife>Until someone slits your throat in your sleep... try to
sleep while trembling in fear.
